## Foundation

This codebase is built on Bitcoin Core v27 (MIT License) and the XMSS
reference implementation (CC0/Public Domain). Those components retain
their original licenses. The Assentian-PQE-specific additions (XMSS
wallet integration, PoUW consensus, P2XMSS/P2XMSSHASH script types,
and related infrastructure) are covered by this BSL-1.1 license.

